title: Which Dog Breed fits your Home
creator: dxsledge Praveen

extendedInfo.description: There are multiple dog breeds across the globe with different characteristics and traits. This app guides you on which dog breed would be suitable for your home, with the help of just 21 questions. The app is carefully designed to help you find the right dog to fit into your family harmoniously.  This app consists of only the top 10 breeds of the American Kennel Club(AKC) of the year 2012 and 2013. Also, a ranking of the dogs based on their compatibility with your family is provided.Download NOW. Absolutely FREE.NOTE: In order to give you a free app and keep developing more free apps in the future, we are integrating a search tool to our application. This will add a few access points to your device (hence the permissions) to direct you to the web search service. Please consider using the search to help us keep creating apps. You may delete the search icon, bookmark and homepage easily. Thank you.
